        <detaileddescription>
<para>Channel numbering for 868 MHz, 915 MHz, and 2450 MHz bands.</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Channel 0 is for 868.3 MHz.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Channels 1-10 are for 906 to 924 MHz with 2 MHz channel spacing.</para>
